/**
*Adore XMLTape Registry
*/

----------------------
Requirements
----------------------
- Java 1.5
- Tomcat 5.5+
- MySQL 4.1+

----------------------
Installation
----------------------
1. Copy adore-xmltape-registry to a location of your choosing

2. Create a new db in MySQL (i.e. CREATE DATABASE tape_registry;)

3. Create a new db user with permissions to new db. (i.e.  GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO tape_registry@localhost IDENTIFIED BY 'pass123' WITH GRANT OPTION;)

4. Configure the following in module.conf:

* module.lib - Define path to lib directory containing project jars (i.e. lib)
* module.src - Define path to src directory containing project source files (i.e. src)
* module.baseurl - Define base url for arcfile registry webapp (i.e. http://library.lanl.gov/aDORe/demo/adore-xmltape-registry/OAIHandler)
* module.db.jdbcurl- Define JDBC URL to arc reg db instance (i.e. jdbc:mysql://127.0.0.1:3306/tape_registry?autoReconnect=true)
* module.db.login - Define db user name (i.e. tape_registry)
* module.db.passwd - Define db user password (i.e. pass123)
* module.admin.email - Define admin e-mail contact (i.e. mailto:rchute@lanl.gov)
* tomcat.home - Define path to tomcat home directory (i.e. /opt/jakarta-tomcat-5.5.9)

5. Run "ant -f build-standalone.xml createdb" to create necessary db tables

6. Run "ant -f build-standalone.xml build" to build project

7. Run "ant -f build-standalone.xml deploy" to copy war to Tomcat WEB-APPS directory.
